**车右前方 3/4 视角**（典型碰撞照，172852-02.png 同款）：
```json
{
  "camera_analysis": {
    "camera_position": "front_right",
    "vehicle_orientation": "车头在屏幕中偏右 (3 点钟方向)",
    "evidence_chain": [
      "车标位于屏幕中右",
      "右后视镜壳体位于屏幕中下，朝向画面外侧",
      "右前大灯 DRL 位于屏幕右上"
    ]
  },
  "primary_view": "front_right",
  "parts": [
    {"part_id": "pillar_a_right", "status": "damaged", "damage_level": "severe", "damage_types": ["deformation"], "confidence": "high", "model_confidence_score": 0.85, "description": "右A柱顶部变形（车头在屏幕中偏右 → front_right 视角 → 屏幕左侧对应车右 A 柱）"},
    {"part_id": "headlight_front_right", "status": "damaged", "damage_level": "moderate", "damage_types": ["breakage"], "confidence": "medium", "model_confidence_score": 0.7, "description": "右前大灯灯罩右侧碎裂（车头在屏幕中偏右 → front_right 视角 → 屏幕中右对应车右大灯）"}
  ]
}
```

只输出 JSON，不要额外文字。
